<div class="container" id= "caption_how">
	<p id="caption">
		You are not an Egyptian unless you know how to play 3arosty.
	</p>
	<button class= "btn btn-default" id="how_text">How To Play</button>
	<%= link_to user_omniauth_authorize_path(:facebook), :class=>'btn btn-primary btn-lg', :id=>'fblogin-link' do %>
    <i class="fa fa-facebook-square fa-lg"></i>
        <h4 id= "loginfacebook"> Login with Facebook </h4>
<% end %>
<div class="panel panel-default" id="how-panel">
  <div class="panel-body">
    	<ul>
    		<li> The Basic idea of the game is to try and guess the object that your opponent is thinking.</li>
    		<li> You are allowed 3 guesses to try and get it right or else you lose.</li>
    		<li> You can ask for hints from your opponent until he declares that has no more hintsto give.</li>
    		<li> Try to think of powerful, yet vague hints to make it harder your opponent.</li>
    		<li> For Example: I am currently thinking of a sofa, a possible hint could be "You can sit on it".</li>
    	</ul>
    	<p id="caption">
			ENJOY.
		</p>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
	
